\id RUT
\h Raɛut
\toc1 Raɛut
\toc2 Raɛut
\toc3 Raɛ.
\mt1 Raɛut
\c 1
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan i di qeṭṭan řquḍat řeḥkamat \add di temmurt\add*, imsar ijj n řaẓ di temmurt. S uyenni iffeɣ ijj n weryaz zi Bayt-Laḥm di Yahudiyya ḥima ad izdeɣ d abarrani deg iyyaren n Mu’ab, netta d temɣart nnes d tnayen n iḥenjiren nnes akides.
\v 2 Aryaz ttřaɣan as \bd Alimalik\bd*, tamɣart nnes ttřaɣan as \bd Naɛumi\bd*, d tnayen n iḥenjiren nnes ttřaɣan asen Maḥlun d Kilyun, \add nitni tuɣa aten d\add* ayt n Ifrata zi Bayt-Laḥm di Yahudiyya. Nitni iwḍen ɣar iyyaren n Mu’ab, qqimen dinni.
\v 3 Alimalik, aryaz n Naɛumi, immut. Teqqim \bd nettat\bd* ak-d tnayen n warraw nnes.
\v 4 Ina iwyen timɣarin n Mu’ab, isem n ict qqaren as Ɛurfa u isem n tenneɣni Raɛut, uca qqiment dinni řqedd n ɛřaḥař ɛecra n iseggʷusa.
\v 5 U mmuten uřa d tnayen nni: Maḥlun d Kilyun. Teqqim temɣart \add weḥḥdes\add*, břa tnayen n warraw nnes u břa aryaz nnes.
\b
\s1 Aɛqab n Naɛumi ak-d Raɛut
\m 
\v 6 Uca teɛdeř Naɛumi ixef nnes ak-d tesřatin nnes, ḥima ad dd-tedweř zeg iyyaren n Mu’ab, maɣar tuɣa tesřa aqa SIDI yarzef i řgens nnes uca iwca asen aɣrum.
\v 7 \add S uyenni\add* teffeɣ nettat ak-d tnayen n tesřatin nnes zeg wemcan mani tuɣa teqqim \add marra řweqt nni\add*. Nitenti ruḥent deg webrid maḥend ad areggʷḥent ɣar temmurt n Yahudiyya.
\v 8 Tenna Naɛumi i tnayen n tesřatin nnes: “Areggʷḥent-i-dd, dewřent-i-dd, kuř icten ɣar taddart n yemmas! SIDI ad akent iwc tamexsiwt \add nnes\add* icewwaren, am mammec tt teggint deg imettan u dayi.
\v 9 SIDI ad yejj ad tafent arraḥet, kuř icten di taddart n weryaz nnes!” Xenni tessudem i-tent uca nitenti ssgeɛɛdent tmijja nsent, sɣuyent,
\v 10 nnant as: “Neccin ad dd-nedweř nican akidem ɣar řgens nnem!”
\v 11 Naɛumi tenna: “Ɛeqbent-i-dd, a yessi! Mayemmi texsent akidi traḥent? Ma \add ɣari\add* deg uɛeddis inu ɛad iḥenjiren nni izemmaren ad dewřen d iryazen i kennint?
\v 12 Ɛeqbent-i-dd, a yessi inu! Ruḥent, minzi necc aqa wsareɣ maḥend ad ɣari yiři ɛad weryaz. Waxxa nniɣ: ‘Necc ɣari ɛad asitem!’, wah, iři ǧiřet-a ad iřiɣ i yijj n weryaz, wah, ad arweɣ iḥenjiren,
\v 13 ma texsent ad trajant ař ɣa mɣaren, ma texsent ad tmenɛent ixef nkent maḥend ad tdewřent i yijj n weryaz? Lla, a yessi! Aqa ameddur inu iffeɣ d amerzag xakent aṭṭas, maɣar iffeɣ-dd ufus n SIDI ḍidd ayi.”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ssgeɛɛdent timijjawin nsent uca arnint ɛad deg iɣuyyan uca Ɛurfa tessudem lallas, maca Raɛut teqqim teřṣeq dayes.
\m 
\v 15 Tenna: “Xzar, tanuṭ nnem aqa tedweř ɣar řgens nnes u ɣar irebbiten nnes. Dweř, teḍfared tanuṭ nnem!”
\v 16 Raɛut tarra-dd xas: “War xafi ttziyyar ḥima ad dayem semḥeɣ uca ad dd-dewřeɣ awarni i weɛrur nnem, minzi mani ɣa tuyured cem, din i ɣa uyureɣ uřa d necc, u mani i ɣa tessensed cem, din i ɣa ssenseɣ uřa d necc, řgens nnem d řgens inu, d AREBBI nnem d AREBBI inu.
\v 17 Mani i ɣa temmted, din i ɣa mmteɣ uřa d necc u din i ɣa ttwaneḍřeɣ uřa d necc. Ejj ad ayi igg SIDI ta d ta uca ad dayes yarni ɛad, minzi mɣir řmewt i d ayi ɣa ibḍan xam!”
\v 18 Ařami teẓra \add Naɛumi\add* belli nettat tegga x tecři, war teqqim tessawař ɛad akides.
\m 
\v 19 Ammu i yuyurent s tnayen idsent ařami iwḍent ɣar Bayt-Laḥm. Umi iwḍent ɣar Baytlaḥm, imsar, aqa marra tandint tenneḥweř di ṭṭweɛ nsent uca nnant \add temɣarin\add*: “Ma d ta d Naɛumi?”
\v 20 Maca nettat tarra-dd xasen tenna: “War d ayi ttřaɣant ‘Naɛumi’ \add ssa d tsawent\add*, \add maca\add* řaɣant ayi: ‘Mara’, maɣar Amzemmar x kuřci igga dayi tarzugi d tameqqrant.\f ◼ \fr 1:20 \fk Mara\ft - man aya ixs ad yini ‘Tamarzagt’.\f*
\v 21 Ffɣeɣ ccureɣ maca SIDI ijja ayi ad dd-areggʷḥeɣ s ifassen xwan. Mayemmi d ayi ttřaɣant \add ɛad\add* ‘Naɛumi’ umi xafi iched SIDI u Amzemmar x kuřci igga ayi min iǧan d aɛeffan?”
\v 22 \add Ammu\add* i tareggʷeḥ Naɛumi ak-d Raɛut, Tamu’abect, tasřift nnes nni dd-idewřen akides zeg iyyaren n Mu’ab. Iwḍent nitenti ɣar Baytl-Laḥm ɣar umezwaru n tmeyra n imendi. \f ◼ \fr 1:22 \fk imendi\ft - niɣ ‘caɛir’ ( الشعير).\f*
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Raɛut deg iyyar n Buɛaz
\m 
\v 1 Naɛumi tuɣa ɣares ijjen zi řaǧ n weryaz nnes, ijj n weryaz s waṭṭas n wagřa, zi řaǧ n Alimalik, ttřaɣan as Buɛaz. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Mt. 1:5\x*
\v 2 Tenna Raɛut Tamu’abect i Naɛumi: “Ejj ayi ad ffɣeɣ ɣar iyyar ad ssmuneɣ tidrin awarni i wenni i ɣa yafeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnes.” Uca nettat tarra-dd xas: “Uyur, yeǧi!” \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Lawi 19:9; 23:22, Aɛwd. 24:19\x*
\m 
\v 3 Raɛut tuyur uca tusa-dd din, tessmuna awarni i yinni imejjaren. Uca imsar, tewḍa as-dd tesɣart n yeyyar n Buɛaz wenni zi řaǧ n Alimalik.
\v 4 U xzar, yusa-dd Buɛaz zi Bayt-Laḥm, inna i yinni imejjaren: “SIDI akidwem!” Nitni arrin-dd xas: “SIDI ad cek ibarek!”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna Buɛaz i umsexxar nnes wenni tuɣa x yinni imejjaren: “Umi tegga yeǧis taḥenjirt nni?”
\v 6 Amsexxar wenni tuɣa x yinni imejjaren, yarra-dd xas, inna: “Nettat d taḥenjirt Tamu’abect i dd-yusin ak-d Naɛumi zeg iyyar n Mu’ab.
\v 7 Nettat tenna: ‘Ejj ayi ad ssmuneɣ tidrin u ad yarweɣ tidrin ɣar icuwwafen \add n imendi\add* awarni i yinni imejjaren!’ Ammu i dd-tusa uca teqqim zeg uteffu n řḥař ař řexxu. Drus waha i teqqim di taddart.”
\m 
\v 8 Buɛaz inna i Raɛut: “Sḥes ɣari, a yeǧi! War třeqqḍed uřa ɣar ijj n yeyyar nneɣni, war ttaggʷej zi ssa, maca qqim tudsed ɣar temsexxarin inu.
\v 9 \add Tebbet\add* tiṭṭawin nnem deg iyyar aya mani mejjaren, uyur awarni asent. Necc ɛeřmeɣ i imsexxaren inu, war cem ttḥidin. \add Mařa\add* teffuded, tzemmared ad tuyured ɣar iqubac ad teswed zi min d yuymen imsexxaren.”
\v 10 Nettat tewḍa x wudem nnes uca tuḍar ɣar temmurt, tenna as: “Mayemmi ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, aqa cek tbedded akidi, \add waxxa\add* necc d tabarranit?”
\v 11 Buɛaz yarra-dd xas, inna: “Aqa nnan ayi nican marra min teggid i lallam awarni i řmewt n weryaz nnem, mammec teggid tsemḥed di babam d yemmam d temmurt nnem mani txeřqed uca tuyured ɣar ijj n řgens i war t tessined qbeř.
\v 12 Ad cem ixeǧeṣ SIDI n Israil tasexxart nnem \add taṣebḥant\add* i teggid uca ad am dd-tas řmunet teccur zi SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, sadu ifriwen nnes i dd-tusid maḥend ad dinni tedduryed.” \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Aɛwd. 32:11; Izhd. 36:8; 57:2; 91:4\x*
\v 13 Nettat tenna: “Ejj ayi ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, a sidi inu, minzi tessfewwjed xafi, tessiwřed ɣar wuř n tayya nnec, waxxa necc war ǧiɣ am uřa d ict zi tiyya nnec.”
\m 
\v 14 Ɣar řḥař n macca inna as Buɛaz: “As-dd da uca ecc zeg weɣrum, sisen ařeqquz nnem di řxeǧ!” Nettat teqqim zzat i yinni imejjaren uca iwca as netta tiɣwawin, tecca tejjiwen, iceṭṭ xas ɛad.
\v 15 Ařami tekkar ḥima ad tessmun tidrin, iɛřem Buɛaz i imsexxaren nnes: “Ejj i-tt ad tessmun jar icuwwafen \add n imendi\add* u war tt tesseḥqaram ca!
\v 16 Ɣeḍřem as-dd cwayt cwayt zi tqebbiḍin uca jjem tt \add di tammurt\add*, uca jjem tt ad tessmun aya, war tt tzawarem.”
\m 
\v 17 Uca nettat tuɣa třeqqeḍ deg iyyar nni ař tameddit. Xenni tṣeffa min tuɣa teřqeḍ. Tuɣa ɛřaḥař řqedd n ijj n ifa n imendi.
\v 18 Nettat tessmun i-t, tudef ɣar tendint uca teẓra lallas min tuɣa teřqeḍ. Tejbed \add ɛawed\add* min tuɣa iceṭṭen zi macca nnes tameqqrant uca tewca as t.
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* tesseqsa lallas: “Mani třeqḍed ass-a u mani txedmed? Ad ittwabarek wenni tuɣa akidem ibedden!” Uca nettat tḥaja as i lallas wi i ɣar tuɣa texdem, tenna: “Aryaz i ɣar xedmeɣ ass-a ttřaɣan as Buɛaz.”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* tenna Naɛumi i tesřift nnes: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI wenni war ikkisen tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren zeg yinni iddaren d yinni immuten!” Tenna as Naɛumi \add ɛawed\add*: “Aryaz nni zzayneɣ, netta d ijj zeg imefdiyyen nneɣ \add inni zemmaren ad sɣen afedday\add*.” \f ◼ \fr 2:20 \fk amefdi - imefdiyyen\ft - wenni izemmaren ad ifekk afday u ad idweř ɛawed ɣar twacunt i ɣar iǧa wefday d agřa n zic.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt Lawi 25:26, 48, 49\x*
\v 21 Raɛut, Tamu’abect, tenna: “Netta inna ayi ɛad: ‘Qqim ɣar imsexxaren nni ɣari iǧan, ař ɣa kemmřen ad ssmunen marra tamegra nni ɣari iǧan.’”
\v 22 Tenna Naɛumi i tesřift nnes Raɛut: “Mliḥ, a yeǧi, mařa teffɣed cem ak-d temsexxarin nnes, xenni war iǧi wi cem i ɣa ihewřen deg iyyar nneɣni.”
\v 23 Raɛut teqqim tudes i temsexxarin n Buɛaz ḥima ad tessmun \add tidrin\add*, ařami teqḍa tmeyra n imendi d tmeyra n irden uca teqqim \add tezdeɣ\add* ɣar lallas.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Raɛut d Buɛaz x unedrar
\m 
\v 1 Uca lallas Naɛumi tenna as: “A yeǧi, ma tuɣa war ttexseɣ ad am afeɣ amcan n řaman ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ?
\v 2 Ma war iǧi Buɛaz, i ɣar tuɣa cem jar temsexxarin nnes, d ijjen zi raǧ nneɣ? Xzar, ass-a ɣar tmeddit, ad izzuzar imendi deg unedrar.
\v 3 Sird, dhen ixef nnem uca yarḍ taqendurt nnem, xenni hwa-dd ɣar unedrar! War seccan ixef nnem i weryaz ař ɣa yiři icca iswa.
\v 4 Mařa iraḥ ad iṭṭeṣ, ad tiři ad tarzud amcan mani izzeř. Adef \add xenni\add* ɣar din, tɛarrid x dduri x iḍaren nnes uca zzeř dinni! Netta ad am yini \add xenni\add*, min ittxeṣṣa ad t tegged.”
\v 5 Nettat tarra-dd xas: “Marra min d ayi teqqared, ad t ggeɣ.”
\m 
\v 6 Nettat tehwa ɣar unedrar uca tegga amenni qaɛ min tuɣa d as tenna lallas.
\v 7 \add Řami\add* icca iswa Buɛaz, ifarḥ wuř nnes, ikkar yuyur, ḥima ad izzeř ɣar ṭṭarf n ijj n uɛurric n tqebbiḍin \add n imendi\add*. \add Xenni\add* tusa-dd břa řḥess, tɛarra \add x dduri\add* ɣar iḍaren nnes uca tezzeř.
\v 8 Ɣar wezyen n ǧiřet innexřeɛ weryaz nni, inneqřeb, uca xzar, ict n temɣart tuɣa tezzeř ɣar iḍaren nnes.
\v 9 Netta inna: “Min teɛnid cem?” Nettat tarra-dd xas: “Necc d Raɛut, tayya nnec. Egg maca afriw nnec x tayya nnec, maɣar cek d wenni izemmaren ad ayi ifdi.” \f ◼ \fr 3:9 \fk ifdi\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Aɛwd. 23:1; 27:20; Ḥiz. 16:8\x*
\v 10 Inna netta: “Tettwabarked cem zi SIDI, a yeǧi! \add Řexxu\add* deg uneggar teggid tamexsiwt nnem icewwaren mahu s min teggid deg umezwaru, maɣar cem war tuzziřed awarni i iɛezriyyen, imezřaḍ niɣ ayt n bu wagřa.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* yeǧi, war tteggʷed ca! Marra min ɣa tinid, ad am t ggeɣ, maɣar qaɛ wi da di tewwart \add n tendint\add* n řgens inu issen, aqa cem d ict n temɣart temḥeḍ.
\v 12 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, d tidett necc d ijj n umefdi, maca din ɛad ijj n umefdi nneɣni, wenni d am itteɛnan ktar xafi necc.
\v 13 Seɛdu ǧiřet-a da. Mařa imsar tiwecca di ṣṣbeḥ, netta ixs ad xam ifdi, mliḥ, \add xenni\add* ejj i-t ad ifdi, maca mařa netta war ixs ad cem ifdi, xenni necc ad xam fdiɣ, s tidett xenni am iddar SIDI. Qqim zzeř ař tiwecca.”
\m 
\v 14 \add Ammu\add* i teqqim tezzeř ɣar iḍaren nnes ař tiwecca uca qbeř ma izemmar ijj ad iẓar wenneɣni, tekkar, \add maɣar\add* netta inna: “War tᵉttiři tᵉttwassnen, aqa ict n temɣart tuɣa tusa-dd ɣar unedrar”
\v 15 Netta inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Ksi tacḍaḍt i zi třeḥḥfed, ṭṭef i-tt!” Uca netta iccur i-tt s setta n \add řeqyasat\add* n imendi uca issarbu tt xas. Xenni yudef ɣar tendint.
\m 
\v 16 Tusa-dd nettat ɣar lallas u tanita tesseqsa: “Min teɛnid cem, a yeǧi?” Nettat tḥaja as marra min kis igga weryaz \add nni\add*. \f ◼ \fr 3:16 \fk Min teɛnid cem, a yeǧi?\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Mammec teǧid, a yeǧi?’\f*
\v 17 Tenna: “Setta n \add řeqyas-a\add* n imendi iwca ayi ten, maɣar netta inna: ‘Cem war teggured ca ɣar lallam s ifassen ixwan.’”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* tenna \add Naɛumi\add*: “Raja, a yeǧi, qqim \add da\add* ař ɣa tessned mammec ɣa teffeɣ tmesřact. Minzi aryaz \add nni\add* war ittareyyiḥ ca ař dd-issuffeɣ tamesřact ɛad ass-a ɣar uneggar nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Buɛaz ifdi iyyar n Alimilik uca imřec ak-d Raɛut
\m 
\v 1 Buɛaz igeɛɛed ɣar tewwart n tendint uca iqqim dinni. U xzar, iɛdu-dd umefdi, wenni xef tuɣa issiweř Buɛaz. Netta inna as: “A cek, diha, as-dd ɣar ṭṭarf \add n webrid\add* u teqqimed danita!” Yusa-dd ɣar ṭṭarf \add n webrid\add* uca iqqim.
\v 2 Yiwi-dd Buɛaz ɛecra n yeryazen zeg imɣaren n tendint, inna: “Qimem-dd danita!”, uca qqimen.
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna i umefdi: “Naɛumi tenni dd-iɛeqben zi temmurt n Mu’ab texs ad tezzenz takirat n yeyyar i tuɣa ɣar umatneɣ Alimalik.
\v 4 Necc xemmeɣ, xseɣ ad cek xas xebbareɣ uca ad ac iniɣ: Seɣ i-tt zzat n yinni i da iqqimen u zzat n imɣaren n řgens. Mařa texsed ad tt tefdid, fdi tt u mařa war texsed ad tt tefdid, ini ayi t ḥima ad ssneɣ, minzi war da ḥed izemmar ad tt ifdi mɣir cek niɣ d necc, u necc i iǧan awarni ac.” \add Xenni\add* inna netta: “Necc ad tt fdiɣ.”\f ◼ \fr 4:4 \fk tefdid ... fdi ... ifdi\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*
\m 
\v 5 Buɛaz yarni inna: “Deg wass i di i ɣa tesɣed iyyar zeg ufus n Naɛumi, \add xenni\add* ad tesɣed akides uřa d Raɛut, Tamu’abect, tamɣart n wenni immuten, ḥima ad teḥḍid isem n umettin x tesɣart nnes n řwart.”
\v 6 Inna umefdi: “\add Xenni\add* necc war zemmareɣ ad t fdiɣ, ḥima war ttḍiyyɛeɣ tasɣart inu. Fdi \add t\add* cek i yixef nnec min xafi maḥend ad t fdiɣ, maɣar necc war zemmareɣ ad t fdiɣ.”
\m 
\v 7 Ammu tuɣa tteggen inni n zzman umi ggin ad beddřen \add iyyar\add* jar asen niɣ umi t fdin, aqa, ḥima ad tewced tamesřact zzat i wudem n marra Israil, aqa aryaz ittekkes sandala nnes uca ittic i-tt i jjar nnes. D man aya tuɣa iǧan di Israil. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Aɛwd. 25:7\x*
\v 8 Amefdi inna i Buɛaz: “Seɣ i-t i yixef nnec!” Uca netta ikkes sandala nnes.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* Buɛaz inna i marra imɣaren u i marra řgens: “Kenniw d řechud deg wass-a, aqa necc, marra min \add iǧan\add* n Alimalik u marra min \add iǧan\add* n Kilyun u n Maḥlun, sɣiɣ t zeg ufus n Naɛumi.
\v 10 Uřa d Raɛut, Tamu’abect, tamɣart n Maḥlun, iwyeɣ tt d tamɣart, ḥima ad iqqim isem n wenni immuten x tesɣart n řwart nnes, maḥend isem n wenni immuten war ittekkes jar aytmac u zi tewwart n wemcan n tzeddiɣt nnes. Deg wass-a aqa kenniw d řechud.” *
\b
\m 
\v 11 Marra řgens nni iǧan di tewwart \add n tendint\add* d imɣaren nnan:
\m “Neccin d řechud! Iři SIDI ad yegg tamɣart nni i d ɣa yadfen ɣar taddart nnec am Raḥil d Liya, tinni zzaysent s tnayen tᵉttwagg teddart n Israil. Egg s cḍaret di Ifrata uca ad ittwabarreḥ isem \add nnec\add* di Bayt-Laḥm! \f ◼ \fr 4:11 \fk Raḥil d Liya\ft - nitenti d timɣarin n Yaɛqub,\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Amz. 29:32-35; 30:1-25; 35:17, 18\x*
\v 12 Taddart nnec tegga am taddart n Fariṣ, wenni turuw-dd Tamar i Yahuda, zeg warraw i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI zi tebřiɣt-a.” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Amz. 38:29; 1 Im. 2:4; Mt. 1:3\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 Buɛaz yiwi Raɛut uca nettat tedweř d tamɣart nnes uca yudef xas uca SIDI iwca as ad teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd ijj n uḥenjir.
\v 14 Uca nnant timɣarin i Naɛumi: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI wenni war cem ijjin ass-a nhřa ijj n umefdi. Iři ad ittwabarreḥ isem nnes di Israil!
\v 15 Ad ɣarwem yiři am wenni dd-issfaqen řeɛmar nnem uca ad cem iṣun x tewsar nnem, maɣar tasřift nnem, tenni cem ittexsen, turuw i-t-i-dd, aqa nettat teḥřa x sebɛa n iḥenjiren.”
\m 
\v 16 Naɛumi teksi aḥenjir, tessars i-t x idmaren nnes u tedweř tessyam i-t.
\v 17 Tajjarin wcint as ijj n yisem, nnant: “I Naɛumi ittwarwuw as-dd ijj n uḥenjir!”, u ggin as Ɛubid. Netta d babas n Yassa, babas n Dawud.
\b
\s1 Řejdud n Dawud
\m 
\v 18 \bd Ina d inni dd-ittwarwen zi Fariṣ:\bd* Fariṣ ijja-dd Ḥaṣrun, \x ◘ \xo 4:18 \xt 1 Im. 2:5; Mt. 1:3\x*
\m 
\v 19 Ḥaṣrun ijja-dd Ram, Ram ijja-dd Ɛamminadab,\x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Mt. 1:4\x*
\m 
\v 20 Ɛamminadab ijja-dd Naḥcun, Naḥcun ijja-dd Salmun, \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt 1 Im. 2:11\x*
\m 
\v 21 Salmun ijja-dd Buɛaz, Buɛaz ijja-dd Ɛubid,\x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt Mt. 1:5\x*
\m 
\v 22 Ɛubid ijja-dd Yassa d Yassa ijja-dd Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Mt. 1:6\x* 
